    <a name="02500201800014" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478" tl="HOTTP3610">锡安</a>​的​<a name="02500201800010" ll="SDBH:חֹומָה:000001" tl="HOTTP3610">城墙</a>​啊​，​愿​你​<a name="02500201800026;02500201800030" ll="SDBH:יֹומָם:000000;SDBH:לַיְלָה:000000">日夜</a>​<a name="02500201800024" ll="SDBH:דִּמְעָה:000000">泪</a>​<a name="02500201800016" ll="SDBH:ירד:000008">流</a>​如​<a name="02500201800022" ll="SDBH:נַחַל:000000">河</a>​，​<a name="02500201800032" ll="SDBH:אַל:000000">不</a>​<a name="02500201800034">让</a>​自己​<a name="02500201800036" ll="SDBH:פּוּגָה:000000">休息</a>​，​你​<a name="02500201800044;02500201800046" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000005;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">眼</a>​<a name="02500201800044;02500201800046" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000005;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">中</a>​<a name="02500201800044;02500201800046" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000005;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">的</a>​<a name="02500201800044;02500201800046" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000005;SDBH:עַיִן:000000">瞳人</a>​也​<a name="02500201800040" ll="SDBH:אַל:000000">不</a>​<a name="02500201800042" ll="SDBH:דמם:000001">歇息</a>​。
    
